## Design Requirements

### Shop Homepage (`shop/page.tsx`)

**Layout Structure:**
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Hero Section                           │
│  "Shop Nail Products & Inspiration"     │
│  Brief intro text                       │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Category Grid (3-4 columns)            │
│  ┌──────┐ ┌──────┐ ┌──────┐ ┌──────┐  │
│  │ Xmas │ │Winter│ │ Fall │ │Trendy│  │
│  └──────┘ └──────┘ └──────┘ └──────┘  │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Featured Products (carousel)           │
│  3-4 products visible                   │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Why Shop With Us (optional text)      │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Hero Section:**
- H1: "Shop Nail Products" (36-42px, Jeremiah)
- Subtitle: 1-2 lines about curated products
- Use `container-standard`
- Minimal, clean design

**Category Cards:**
- Image background (nail art from that category)
- Category name overlay (white text, semi-transparent backdrop)
- 3 columns desktop, 2 tablet, 1 mobile
- Hover: slight lift + brightness increase
- 40px gap between cards

---

### Category Page (`shop/[category]/page.tsx`)

**Layout (Vogue-inspired):**
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Category Hero                          │
│  "Christmas Nail Products"              │
│  Short description                      │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Filter Bar (optional)                  │
│  Sort: Price | Popularity | New        │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Product Grid                           │
│  ┌────┐ ┌────┐ ┌────┐ ┌────┐          │
│  │ P1 │ │ P2 │ │ P3 │ │ P4 │          │
│  └────┘ └────┘ └────┘ └────┘          │
│  ┌────┐ ┌────┐ ┌────┐ ┌────┐          │
│  │ P5 │ │ P6 │ │ P7 │ │ P8 │          │
│  └────┘ └────┘ └────┘ └────┘          │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Pagination: 1 / 4                     │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  FAQ Section (if available)            │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Product Grid:**
- **Desktop:** 4 columns (can reduce to 3 if images need more space)
- **Tablet:** 3 columns
- **Mobile:** 2 columns (tight grid) or 1 column (better for images)
- Use `container-wide` wrapper
- 30-40px gap between products

**Grid Spacing (Vogue-style):**
- More padding on sides (use container-wide padding)
- Generous spacing between rows (50-60px)
- Clean, uncluttered feel

