### Product Card (`ProductShowcase.tsx`)

**Design (Vogue-inspired):**
```
┌─────────────────┐
│                 │
│  Product Image  │
│  (square/4:5)   │
│                 │
├─────────────────┤
│ BRAND NAME      │  ← 12px, uppercase, tracking-wide
│ Product Title   │  ← 16-18px, Boriboon font
│ $29.99          │  ← 16px, bold
│ ★★★★☆ (23)     │  ← Optional ratings
└─────────────────┘
```

**Card Details:**
- **Image:** Square or 4:5 ratio, object-cover
- **Hover:** Scale image 1.05, lift card
- **Brand:** Uppercase, 12px, letter-spacing wide, light gray
- **Title:** 16-18px, Boriboon font, 2 line clamp
- **Price:** Bold, 16px, #252220
- **Border:** 1px solid #e5e7eb
- **Padding:** 16px
- **Background:** white

**Mobile Adjustments:**
- Keep 2 columns for compact look
- OR switch to 1 column for better visibility
- Reduce font sizes slightly (14-16px)
- Maintain 48px touch targets

