### Single Product Page (`shop/[category]/[productId]/page.tsx`)

**Layout:**
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  ┌─────────────────┬─────────────────────────┐ │
│  │                 │                         │ │
│  │  Product Image  │  Product Info           │ │
│  │  Gallery        │                         │ │
│  │  (50%)          │  - Brand                │ │
│  │                 │  - Title                │ │
│  │  ┌───┬───┬───┐  │  - Price                │ │
│  │  │ 1 │ 2 │ 3 │  │  - Rating               │ │
│  │  └───┴───┴───┘  │  - Description          │ │
│  │  Thumbnails     │  - Features/Benefits    │ │
│  │                 │  - BUY NOW button       │ │
│  │                 │  - Affiliate link       │ │
│  └─────────────────┴─────────────────────────┘ │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Product Description (full width)               │
│  - How to use                                   │
│  - Ingredients/specs                            │
│  - Care instructions                            │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Related Products (4 cards, carousel)           │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Image Gallery:**
- Main image: Large, zoom on hover
- Thumbnails below: 4-5 images
- Click thumbnail to change main image
- Mobile: Swipeable gallery

**Product Info:**
- Brand name (14px, uppercase, gray)
- Product title (28-32px, Jeremiah)
- Price (24px, bold)
- Star rating (if available)
- Short description (18px, Crimson Text)
- Key features (bullet list)
- **BUY NOW button:**
  - Border: 2px solid #252220
  - Padding: 16px 48px
  - Hover: Fill #252220, text white
  - Link to affiliate URL

**Mobile Layout:**
- Stack vertically (image top, info below)
- Gallery swipeable
- Sticky "BUY NOW" at bottom (optional)

