## Image Handling

### Product Images
- **Category page:** Lazy load (Pinterest-style)
- **Single product:** Load main image immediately
- **Thumbnails:** Load on demand
- **Format:** WebP preferred
- **Sizes:** Responsive srcset

### Image Optimization
- Product cards: 400x400px (or 400x500px for 4:5)
- Single product main: 800x800px
- Thumbnails: 100x100px
- Compression: High quality but optimized

---

## Affiliate Link Handling

**Button Design:**
```html
<a href="affiliate-url" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">
  <button>
    BUY NOW ON AMAZON
  </button>
</a>
```

- Opens in new tab
- Clear CTA text
- Nofollow for SEO
- Track clicks (optional analytics)

