## Mobile Optimizations

### Category Page
- Switch to 1-2 column grid
- Larger product images
- Stack filters vertically
- Reduce gaps to 16px

### Product Page
- Stack gallery and info
- Swipeable image gallery
- Sticky "Buy Now" button at bottom
- Collapse long descriptions

