## Typography in Shop

### Product Titles
- Font: Boriboon (product font)
- Size: 16-18px on cards, 28-32px on product page
- Weight: 500-600
- Line clamp: 2 lines max on cards

### Prices
- Font: Boriboon or Crimson Text
- Size: 16-18px on cards, 24px on product page
- Weight: Bold (700)
- Format: $29.99 or $29 (no decimals if .00)

### Descriptions
- Font: Crimson Text
- Size: 16-18px
- Line height: 1.6-1.7
- Max width: 800px for readability

